{"tid":1014603,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"唐文龍常往返美國只為與父母吃飯　孝順Michael：人最恐懼就是寂寞","createTime":"2019-02-09T10:35:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-09T19:54:14.000Z","uid":130626,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"399d5bca3a3959ede358f1fdf6e9af60244be34c","tid":1014603,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T10:35:27.000Z","msg":"最近為「長者家」拍攝關愛短片的唐文龍（Michael），真情分享與家人的相處。唐文龍的父母長居在美國，而爸爸近年因骨質疏鬆而導致身體不適，唐文龍則隻身在香港工作，雖然與家人分隔兩地，但孝順的唐文龍，經常抽時間飛到美國探望家人。唐文龍感慨父母年紀漸大，認為人最恐懼的就是獨自一人，因此希望能多陪伴父母。<br />\n現年49歲的Michael與父母及哥哥分居在香港及美國，哥哥住在三藩市，父母居住於西雅圖，由此令事業以香港為基地的他大感無奈。<br />\n然而，Michael的爸爸近年患上骨質疏鬆症，而且常感到身體不適：「但也因此多了見面，這段時間吃飯的次數，快要比我們一生所吃的多。」<br />\nMichael指，與家人吃家常便飯對很多人來說或許是件微不足道的事：「但對我而言卻是既難得又很溫馨，別具意義！」<br />\n由於Michael的父母覺得自己並非很老：「因而他們不希望被人照顧，覺得自己比別人精神，所以需要花時間去說服他們。」他又指：「爸爸未患有骨質疏鬆前，其實也很健康。現時請了兩位姑娘照顧他，每星期會來3至4次，每次過來數小時以觀察爸爸做運動。」<br />\nMichael指自己是個不願認老的人：「我想人對老的恐懼是因為做不到自己本來做到的事，包括行為、行動及記性，只有關心你的人才能真正的包容、付出以及去愛。」他續指：「我覺得人最恐懼的就是寂寞，獨自一人。」<br />\n為免令父母感到寂寞，工作忙碌的Michael特意抽更多時間往返美國，陪在父母身旁，令他們不會感到孤單，十分孝順！<br />\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2265000/2267626/Tong_thumb_20190208_S_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2265000%2F2267626%2FTong_thumb_20190208_S_1024.jpg&h=59c62230&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2265000/2267626/Tong_1_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2265000%2F2267626%2FTong_1_1024.jpg&h=404a35f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2265000/2267626/Tong_2_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2265000%2F2267626%2FTong_2_1024.jpg&h=fd805936&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2265000/2267626/Tong_3_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2265000%2F2267626%2FTong_3_1024.jpg&h=201680b3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f6b60787d8b4f0aec82408c13c76dfb10464c865","tid":1014603,"uid":1067,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T10:36:47.000Z","msg":"所以要同垃圾桶影相？"},{"pid":"c732de93171849850c1d2f53fa66832ada538785","tid":1014603,"uid":3122,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T10:39:46.000Z","msg":"老啦龍仔"},{"pid":"2349610d65d45829489a8ca7fa6f06add05b5de7","tid":1014603,"uid":12558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T10:40:15.000Z","msg":"已經49歳😮"},{"pid":"3bb5dddb763651f1dd4c077147c0cfd5aa2e1648","tid":1014603,"uid":132587,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T10:41:26.000Z","msg":"少番d姿粉味既話真係man到無敵"},{"pid":"e709f70331fb3fb2b752c0722dfa2159c384c7c6","tid":1014603,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T10:52:37.000Z","msg":"占占<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16a52c20ab1e3ed4cc2696add79fc6ea81c9721f","tid":1014603,"uid":67208,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T10:57:51.000Z","msg":"以前條眉好似冇咁怪"},{"pid":"f8d16af714b29504dd7d2f9d2a48845a01c27314","tid":1014603,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"16a52c20ab1e3ed4cc2696add79fc6ea81c9721f","tid":1014603,"uid":67208,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T10:57:51.000Z","msg":"以前條眉好似冇咁怪"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T19:54:14.000Z","msg":"我都覺"}]}